to create a user account into clowder.

example to run:

1) 
docker run --rm -it -e "PASSWORD=youpassword" -e "EMAIL_ADDRESS=youremailaddress" -e "HOSTIP=hostipofmongo" --name create-useraccount browndog/create-useraccount bash

2)
docker run --rm -it -e "FIRST_NAME=John" -e "LAST_NAME=Smith" -e "PASSWORD=yourpassword" -e "EMAIL_ADDRESS=youremailaddress" -e "HOSTIP=hostipofmongo" --name create-useraccount browndog/create-useraccount bash
